附魔 id 冲突
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Duplicate enchantment id! class fox.spiteful.forbidden.enchantments.EnchantmentConsuming and class matteroverdrive.enchantment.EnchantmentOverclock Enchantment ID:69

forbidden 或者 matteroverdrive 的配置文件中，把 69 改成别的数值就行了

也就是 .minecraft\config\MatterOverdrive\Matter Overdrive.cfg 中

enchantments {
    I:Overclock=69
}

69 改成别的数值就行
